==English==
===Adjective===
'''miniscule'''

#Variant spelling of '''[[minuscule]]''' (''see'' '''Usage notes''' ''below'')

====Usage notes====
*The spelling '''minuscule''' is the original and etymologically precise spelling.  The spelling '''miniscule''', which has perhaps arisen by confusion with '''[[mini]]''', is generally considered to be incorrect, but is in very widespread use.  Careful speakers and writers prefer '''minuscule'''.
*At the time of writing (29 September 2005), the number of hits in the printed works listed in [http://print.google.com/ Google Print] for '''minuscule''' outnumbers those for '''miniscule''' by a large amount (by 24,400 to 7,250, a ratio of about 77:23).  In contrast, the numbers of hits on Google are 2,530,000 to 1,940,000, a ratio of about 57:43.